description: Blond-haired, blue-eyed, 21-year-old Geoff hails from Northern California, and he’s quite the sports buff, but wrestling was his concentration. These days he enjoys riding his motorcycle, and taking in good weather. “When I first realized I had a larger than average penis, I was checking out what the other guys had to offer in the locker room,” says Geoff. “My dick is pretty straight. It doesn’t curve or anything, and other than that it’s cut,” adds Geoff. “I would say I have sex pretty often; probably every other day. My ideal type of sex changes, but I have to say I like it slow. Slow sex is good!”
title: Geoff
